    {
      "id": "189d3f62",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3138,
      "width": 1540,
      "height": 21.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f59f00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "THE 8 RULES OF LOCATION IN ATTENDEASE",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "f67b76a0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3162,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "1. Permission = 'While Using App' ONLY \u2014 never 'Always'",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "5a750a5e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3184,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "2. Location read TWICE per day max \u2014 check-in (~30s) + check-out (~30s)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "df38b336",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3206,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "3. Pre-warm GPS on screen load \u2014 don't wait for button tap",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "86dac0a1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 3228,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "4. Store coordinates ALWAYS \u2014 even WFH (no validation, but log it)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "21793a5e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 3162,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "5. Accuracy threshold: \u226450m perfect \u00b7 50\u2013100m warn + flag \u00b7 >100m retry",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "39da21af",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 3184,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "6. Never tell employee which mock detection layer caught them",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "e2b23f48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 3206,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e2e8f0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "7. Velocity check EVERY check-in server-side \u2014 your strongest iOS anti-spoof",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "d1c85d3d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 3228,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 15.0,
